title: What Penises REALLY Want
itunes:title: What Penises REALLY Want
itunes:subtitle: What Penises REALLY Want
description:
2016 is coming to a close, so it’s time to talk about the state of your sex life. What’s holding you back from having the sex and relationships you crave? On today’s show, we share advice to help you face those blocks head on.

What do you do when your partner’s oral sex technique is a little too… Intense? How do you recover from a toxic relationship without falling into the same hole? And is there really a correlation between weight and penis size? Emily and Menace tackle these problems and more, plus, give you a little insight into what their goals are for 2017. Don’t miss out!


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
